  "text": "where the exponential term accounts for a crowding effect which makes the alignment increasingly more difficult when the density becomes too large. A more detailed derivation of system (2) and possible other alignment terms f is found in [CITATION_1] . The model contains the two parameters ε and α denoting the strengths of diffusion and alignment respectively. By rescaling both time and space by α, t = αt,x = αx we arrive at the rescaled problem",
